    {
      "start": 347.37,
      "end": 351.11,
      "text": "이 팀 로스에 대한 이야기도 차차 풀어봐야 되겠죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 351.11,
      "end": 359.21,
      "text": "He's a British actor and producer, and he is part of a group of prominent British actors known as the Brit Pack."
